<div style="position: relative; top: 25px; clear: both; "><div style="height: 64px; margin-bottom: 5px;">  <h2 style="float: right;">Efreet</h2>  <img src="images/creatures/efreet.gif"/></div><div style="margin-bottom: 35px; clear: both;">  <p>The Efreet are the merciless leaders of the green djinns. Surpassing their lesser brethren both in power and in cruelty, the Efreet are truly terrible opponents who love to use their awesome powers to spread havoc among their enemies or sometimes among their own kind. The disdain they feel towards all other sentient races is second only to the undying hatred they feel towards their blue-skinned relatives, the Marid.</p>  <p>Efreet have 550 hitpoints. They cannot be paralyzed. Moreover, they are strong against death, earth, energy and fire damage. On the other hand, they are weak against holy and ice damage. These creatures can neither be summoned nor convinced. In addition, they are able to sense invisible creatures.</p>  <p>Efreet yield 410 experience points. They carry gold coins, pears, royal spears, strong mana potions and sometimes other items with them.</p>  </div></div>